{"tha-ap440:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap440:0.2":"Ekaviharivagga ","tha-ap440:0.3":"Haritakadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap440:1.1":"“Haritakam amalakam, ","tha-ap440:1.2":"ambajambuvibhitakam; ","tha-ap440:1.3":"Kolam bhallatakam billam, ","tha-ap440:1.4":"sayameva haramaham. ","tha-ap440:2.1":"Disvana pabbharagatam, ","tha-ap440:2.2":"jhayim jhanaratam munim; ","tha-ap440:2.3":"Abadhena apilentam, ","tha-ap440:2.4":"adutiyam mahamunim. ","tha-ap440:3.1":"Haritakam gahetvana, ","tha-ap440:3.2":"sayambhussa adasaham; ","tha-ap440:3.3":"Khadamattamhi bhesajje, ","tha-ap440:3.4":"byadhi passambhi tavade. ","tha-ap440:4.1":"Pahinadaratho buddho, ","tha-ap440:4.2":"anumodamakasi me; ","tha-ap440:4.3":"‘Bhesajjadanenimina, ","tha-ap440:4.4":"byadhivupasamena ca. ","tha-ap440:5.1":"Devabhuto manusso va, ","tha-ap440:5.2":"jato va annajatiya; ","tha-ap440:5.3":"Sabbattha sukhito hotu, ","tha-ap440:5.4":"ma ca te byadhimagama’. ","tha-ap440:6.1":"Idam vatvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap440:6.2":"sayambhu aparajito; ","tha-ap440:6.3":"Nabham abbhuggami dhiro, ","tha-ap440:6.4":"hamsarajava ambare. ","tha-ap440:7.1":"Yato haritakam dinnam, ","tha-ap440:7.2":"sayambhussa mahesino; ","tha-ap440:7.3":"Imam jatim upadaya, ","tha-ap440:7.4":"byadhi me nupapajjatha. ","tha-ap440:8.1":"Ayam pacchimako mayham, ","tha-ap440:8.2":"carimo vattate bhavo; ","tha-ap440:8.3":"Tisso vijja sacchikata, ","tha-ap440:8.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap440:9.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap440:9.2":"bhesajjamadadim tada; ","tha-ap440:9.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap440:9.4":"bhesajjassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap440:10.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap440:10.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap440:10.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap440:11.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap440:11.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap440:11.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap440:12.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap440:12.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap440:12.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap440:13.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma haritakadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap440:14.1":"Haritakadayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}